<section class="content-section" id="overview-section">
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2 class="section-title">Turnover Certificate for Tender for Delhi</h2>
            <div class="content-text">
                <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
                    <p><strong>&#128204; TL;DR - Turnover Certificate for Tender in Delhi Services at a Glance</strong></p>
                    <p>Statutory audit is the legally mandated examination of a company's financial statements by a CA to express an opinion on whether they present a true and fair view. Under Section 139, every company - Pvt Ltd, Public, OPC, Section 8, regardless of turnover - must appoint a turnover certificate for tenderor. The auditor's report is filed with RoC Delhi (IFCI Tower, Nehru Place) along with financial statements. Patron's Delhi CA team provides end-to-end services from auditor appointment through audit execution, CARO 2020 reporting and RoC filing.</p>
                </div>
                <p><div class="table-responsive-wrapper"><table><thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Detail</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr><td>Governing Sections</td><td>CA-Certified Net Worth in INR + Foreign Currency</td></tr>
<tr><td>Mandatory For</td><td>Every company under Companies Act - no turnover exemption</td></tr>
<tr><td>Auditor Appointment</td><td>First: Board within 30 days. Subsequent: AGM for 5-year term</td></tr>
<tr><td>Rotation</td><td>Individual CA: 1x5 years. Firm: 2x5 years. 5-year cooling period</td></tr>
<tr><td>CARO 2020</td><td>21 reporting matters for prescribed companies</td></tr>
<tr><td>Filing</td><td>AOC-4 + MGT-7 with RoC Delhi within 30 days of AGM</td></tr>
<tr><td>Penalty</td><td>Company: Rs 25,000 to Rs 5,00,000. Late filing: Rs 100/day</td></tr>
<tr><td>Delhi RoC</td><td>IFCI Tower, 61 Nehru Place, New Delhi - 110019</td></tr>
</tbody></table></div></p>
                <p><p>Delhi hosts India's largest number of registered companies - 50,000+ active Pvt Ltd companies, listed corporations at Connaught Place, PSUs at Bhikaji Cama Place and government companies. Every one requires turnover certificate for tender. With ICAI's 60-audit cap from April 2026, quality audit firm availability has tightened.</p>
<p>Patron's Delhi CA team provides end-to-end turnover certificate for tender. Learn more about <a href="/turnover-certificate-for-tender">Turnover Certificate for Tender across India</a>. Related: <a href="/turnover-certificate-for-tender">Turnover Certificate for Tender</a> and <a href="/secretarial-audit">Secretarial Audit</a>.</p></p>
                <p>Content is reviewed quarterly for accuracy.</p>
